      <title>一些RE的WriteUP</title>
      <link href="/2024/11/10/%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9BRE%E7%9A%84WriteUP/"/>
      <url>/2024/11/10/%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9BRE%E7%9A%84WriteUP/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>A collection for reverse writeups.</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="BUUCTF-easyre"><a href="#BUUCTF-easyre" class="headerlink" title="BUUCTF_easyre"></a>BUUCTF_easyre</h1><ul><li><p>DIE打开，64位</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/18/gvDl6SAdMExnoaT.png" alt="DIE"></p></li><li><p>IDA打开，映入眼帘的就是flag了</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/18/rPq8tzDfC75QFOA.png" alt="flag"></p></li><li><p>flag：flag{this_Is_a_EaSyRe}</p></li></ul><h1 id="BUUCTF-reverse1"><a href="#BUUCTF-reverse1" class="headerlink" title="BUUCTF_reverse1"></a>BUUCTF_reverse1</h1><ul><li><p>64位</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/18/UGwuKWQqI9B1vyO.png" alt="DIE"></p></li><li><p>IDA查看字符串表，定位关键字符串</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/18/fanxDCzL8ZXl7ou.png" alt="字符串表"></p></li><li><p>找到主函数并按F5，分析</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/18/KtnkjFwml9JM3aq.png" alt="主函数分析"></p></li><li><p>得到flag：flag{hell0_w0rld}</p></li></ul><h1 id="MAZE"><a href="#MAZE" class="headerlink" title="MAZE"></a>MAZE</h1><ul><li><p>来道迷宫题</p></li><li><p>DIE打开，32位</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/21/PZW49enSpEQrXtC.png" alt="DIE"></p></li><li><p>ida打开，找到主函数位置，分析发现关键函数</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/21/fSjnU86WR7rEJwe.png" alt="主函数"></p></li><li><p>进入关键函数，如图。由特征：判断输入的字符是四种情况的哪种 得知这是一道迷宫题（（雾）主函数里的shortest path也是一个提示）</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/21/ZJ9CR4MioISuYQV.png" alt="关键函数"></p></li><li><p>查看v3，发现是地图</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/21/J1b7UchVE3mBla5.png" alt="地图数据"></p></li><li><p>把地图抄到文本里：</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/21/rO3bj7dnVe1BhJS.png" alt="地图"></p></li><li><p>解出迷宫，得到flag：flag{sssssdsssssddddddwawwdwwaaaw}</p></li></ul><h1 id="CTFshow-大吉大利杯-A-Maze-ln"><a href="#CTFshow-大吉大利杯-A-Maze-ln" class="headerlink" title="CTFshow 大吉大利杯 A-Maze-ln"></a>CTFshow 大吉大利杯 A-Maze-ln</h1><ul><li><p>上难度</p></li><li><p>题目maze辨别出是一道迷宫题</p></li><li><p>die打开，32位</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/22/ZsA76KyH5YJiM8R.png" alt="die打开"></p></li><li><p>ida打开，定位到main函数，开始分析，下面是代码</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> __cdecl <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> argc, <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> **argv, <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> **envp)</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">char</span> v3; <span class="comment">// di</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">unsigned</span> __int8 v4; <span class="comment">// bl</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">unsigned</span> __int8 v5; <span class="comment">// dl</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">int</span> i; <span class="comment">// esi</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">char</span> v7; <span class="comment">// al</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">int</span> v8; <span class="comment">// ecx</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">unsigned</span> <span class="type">int</span> j; <span class="comment">// esi</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">char</span> v11; <span class="comment">// [esp-1Ch] [ebp-254h]</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">char</span> v12; <span class="comment">// [esp-18h] [ebp-250h]</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">char</span> v13; <span class="comment">// [esp+0h] [ebp-238h]</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">char</span> v14[<span class="number">256</span>]; <span class="comment">// [esp+8h] [ebp-230h] BYREF</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">char</span> ArgList[<span class="number">256</span>]; <span class="comment">// [esp+108h] [ebp-130h] BYREF</span></span><br><span class="line">  _DWORD v16[<span class="number">11</span>]; <span class="comment">// [esp+208h] [ebp-30h] BYREF</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="number">0xB00E2A69</span>;                          <span class="comment">// 结合后面的分析，这是混淆算法会用到的数据。</span></span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">0x4047D51C</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">2</span>] = <span class="number">0xE7E4D4D6</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">3</span>] = <span class="number">0x7DA1452E</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">4</span>] = <span class="number">0x12843715</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">5</span>] = <span class="number">0x1BCE072B</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">6</span>] = <span class="number">0xE91D79E</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">7</span>] = <span class="number">0xC1AE9D83</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">8</span>] = <span class="number">0xB82921A8</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">9</span>] = <span class="number">0x824856E</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v16[<span class="number">10</span>] = <span class="number">0x1DFB6C0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">memset</span>(v14, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(v14));</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">memset</span>(ArgList, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(ArgList));</span><br><span class="line">  sub_401020(<span class="string">&quot;Do you wanna play a game?\n&quot;</span>, v12);</span><br><span class="line">  sub_401020(<span class="string">&quot;Let&#x27;s play escape game where you have to find a way out. Please enter your way:&quot;</span>, v11);</span><br><span class="line">  sub_401050(<span class="string">&quot;%s&quot;</span>, ArgList);</span><br><span class="line">  v4 = <span class="number">3</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  v5 = <span class="number">0</span>;                                       <span class="comment">// 起点</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> ( <span class="built_in">strlen</span>(ArgList) != <span class="number">34</span> )                  <span class="comment">// 要求输入的字符长度（即路径）为34</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">goto</span> LABEL_22;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span> ( i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="number">34</span>; ++i )</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    v7 = ArgList[i];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">switch</span> ( v7 )                               <span class="comment">// 以下是操作与之对应的字符</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;U&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        v8 = v5;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ( byte_404018[<span class="number">32</span> * v5 + <span class="number">4</span> * v4] != <span class="number">1</span> )</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">goto</span> LABEL_22;</span><br><span class="line">        --v5;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;D&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        v8 = v5;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ( byte_404019[<span class="number">32</span> * v5 + <span class="number">4</span> * v4] != <span class="number">1</span> )</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">goto</span> LABEL_22;</span><br><span class="line">        ++v5;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;L&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        v8 = v5;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ( byte_40401A[<span class="number">32</span> * v5 + <span class="number">4</span> * v4] != <span class="number">1</span> )</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">goto</span> LABEL_22;</span><br><span class="line">        --v4;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;R&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        v8 = v5;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ( byte_40401B[<span class="number">32</span> * v5 + <span class="number">4</span> * v4] != <span class="number">1</span> )</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">goto</span> LABEL_22;</span><br><span class="line">        ++v4;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">default</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">goto</span> LABEL_22;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> ( v4 != <span class="number">4</span> || v5 != <span class="number">7</span> )                     <span class="comment">// 要求v4等于4，v5等于7（即终点）</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">LABEL_22:</span><br><span class="line">    sub_401020(<span class="string">&quot;You&#x27;re stuck!\n&quot;</span>, v13);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> ( sub_401090((<span class="type">int</span>)v16, (<span class="type">int</span>)v14, v8, (<span class="type">int</span>)ArgList) == <span class="number">-1</span> )</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  sub_401020(<span class="string">&quot;Escaped! You see the flag\n&quot;</span>, v3);<span class="comment">// 下面输出flag，但是sub_401090函数加了混淆算法，难以用脚本解决，所以直接运行程序得到flag</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span> ( j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt;= <span class="number">44</span>; ++j )</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Sleep(<span class="number">0xC8</span>u);</span><br><span class="line">    sub_401020(<span class="string">&quot;%c&quot;</span>, v14[j]);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>这里有点反常的是用代数坐标代替了地图上的标记，四个方向的操作和两个坐标都有关联。也就是说，&#x3D;&#x3D;每一步操作不一定就是移动一位&#x3D;&#x3D;（按我的理解）。点开每个操作里的byte数组，可以发现地图。和上面的分析对应的是，迷宫没有外墙结构，并且从起点（3，0）到终点，按照平常想法每个操作走一步是走不了的（一个问题是坐标系信息不知道，另一个是很多地方是没有出路的（三面墙））。</p></li><li><p>所以到这里只能抽象地解决这个问题，用算法实现坐标从（3，0）到（4，7）。这里涉及了算法上经典的（最短）路径问题，我不会了(ToT)，只能参考大佬的脚本。（链接直达：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/2302_79135465/article/details/140347637">https://blog.csdn.net/2302_79135465/article/details/140347637</a>)</p></li><li><p>借助大佬的脚本得到了最终路径：LLDRRDLLLDRDLDDDRRULURRULURRDDDLDR</p></li><li><p>接下来启动靶场，nc输入路径就得到flag：ctfshow{bc98f25c-eace-498e-880f-71b711188eb7}</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/22/uRkBZSEWQGeHP2T.png" alt="连接靶场"></p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
